title: The Keep (1983)
description:
This is an XVID/MP3 encoded version of The Keep based on the Laserdisc rip by Mr Bridger.

There are other encodes of this movie but I found they suffered from low quality or bad deinterlacing problems so I created this version.  It was done with StaxRip with the Field Deinterlace and medium noise reduction filters, 2-pass.

Enjoy!
